Inumaki from #jujutsukaisen!!

actually this is an art trade with the amazing artist @prawnm33 🔥 I Asked what character she would like to me to draw so i was a bit nervous drawing this one since i love her art!

Well, I hope she likes it and I hope you guys like it too!
(btw you will find out the character I choose on her ig later haha)
